ODM party leader Raila Odinga has once again hinted that he will be running for presidency in the 2022 general election. On a day that Kenya was marking the 31st saba saba commemoration, Odinga took to his social media outlining his 15-point agenda for the country under the banner going forward. So, is he launching his fifth bid for the presidency? What his game plan? Duncan Khaemba engaged a section of ODM MPs who are part of Odinga inner circle who have confirmed that indeed Odinga is in the race unless otherwise.
